text: Nias Utara (North Nias) Regency is a regency in North Sumatra province of Indonesia. It has an area of 1,202.78 km2, and a population of 127,244 at the 2010 Census; the latest official estimate (for January 2014) is 132,593. ==Administration== The regency is divided into eleven districts (kecamatan), tabulated below with their areas (in km2) and their 2010 Census populations:Biro Pusat Statistik, Jakarta, 2011. {| class="sortable wikitable" |- !
